  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we belong-- I was baptized in the St.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "John, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's cathedral.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the place where all out Polish king, who lived in Warsaw, go during the-- special corridor to the cathedral for mass, the St.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "John Cathedral.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my father has good relationship and special with couple family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we cannot talk generally, because, you know, you have contact with some business people, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You stick with this people if you trust and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father was-- has good relationship with a family, Melamed and Birnbaum and Landau, a couple of families, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because this was a good relationship, for example, 1930-- 1940, if I remember-- '40, '41, I was with my father on the bat-- bar mitzvah to our [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] friends' family, Mr.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Melamed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was two boys, at the same time, going through the ceremony.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And right now, one of the boys, maybe 65 years old, is in-- [LAUGHS] in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have later, there, I show you the photo, Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Melamed and the one Melamed son still in life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's in the Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other one, brother, died during the war with Arab.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is the '60-something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's the part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, my-- because we was good connected with the people during the war, 1939 and after 1940, I was-- I come back from the army, because I was captured, 17 September, by Soviet Army, on the east.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I come back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I work for some transport company.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after 1940, I was connected with the-- like, I sell good, what was produced in this area, where was ghetto, in Aryan part, for example, the toys.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
